org.tandembrowsing.io

Class Event

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.tandembrowsing.io.Event

  • public class Event
extends java.lang.Object
    Event is a container for passing commands. Event provides also serialization of it self to the XML format and parsing and XML back to the Object presentation.
